00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:02,720
Forgive my indiscretion.

627
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,680
I apologize to you.

628
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:07,160
Come here.

629
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,640
I've thought over and over

