665
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,160
Yang Qi,

666
00:22:44,310 --> 00:22:45,400
you'd better shut up.

667
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,720
Is this something you can ask about?

668
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:47,830
Zhi, Xian,

669
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:48,440
let's go.

