724
00:24:36,830 --> 00:24:37,160
Hurry up!

725
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,350
No, it wasn't me! I didn't eat anything!

726
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,440
Zheng Hu ate them!

727
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,640
I hardly had a piece!

728
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,270
