828
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:52,790
Fortunately, he's a good person.

829
00:27:52,790 --> 00:27:53,240
Right?

830
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:57,070
Baoxia.

831
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:58,920
Tell us the truth.

832
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:00,160
Does Chen Qing

833
00:28:00,310 --> 00:28:01,510
