837
00:28:08,640 --> 00:28:09,920
That Commander was a fake?

838
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,750
He's our master of martial arts.

839
00:28:13,310 --> 00:28:14,030
Zhi

840
00:28:14,240 --> 00:28:16,200
